title: You Have Control Issues
itunes:title: You Have Control Issues
description:
Episode 347 -  You are in control of your life. You and only you! Not your family, spouse, president or any of them. The sooner you realize this and accept responsibility for all that happens in your life, the sooner you can start making real changes in your life.
